This paper is primarily focused on network security and detecting botnets, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves analyzing network behavior and clustering, which could fall under networked systems (cs.NI) and social and information networks (cs.SI). The use of machine learning and community detection could also potentially fall under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data structures (cs.DS).
